extendedInfo.description: If you are Far East Movement's fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check Far East Movement's lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all Far East Movement's lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of Far East Movement's lyrics are here. You can quickly search the lyrics by using the search bar at the top of the page.Hope you guy enjoy using this app as much as I enjoy developing it. :)-------------------------------- Main Features -------------------------------- - Lyrics categorized by album - Show all lyrics - Search lyrics-------------------------------- List of albums -------------------------------- - Folk Music- Animal- Free Wired- Dirty Bass-------------------------------- List of lyrics -------------------------------- - 2 Is Better- 2Gether- 3D- A Beautiful Day- Ain't Coming Down- All Night- Basshead- Boomshake- Candy- Dance Like Michael Jackson- Dirty Bass- Do What I Want- Don't Look Now- Down To Ride- Eyes Never Lie- Fetish- Fighting For Air- Flossy- Fly With U- For The City- Get Offa Me- Get That Money- Girls On The Dance Floor- Go Ape- Hollahey- I Party- If I Die Tomorrow- If I Was You (OMG)- Light Out (Go Crazy)- Like A G6- Little Bird- Live My Life- Live My Life (Party Rock Remix)- Lowridin'- Make Ya Self- Millionaire- No One's Home For The Holidays- Rocketeer- Round Round- She Owns The Night- Show Me Love- So What?- The Good Stuff- Turn Up The Love- Where The Wild Things Are- White Flag- You've Got A Friend
